tweet: @viget99 @JohnnyNeat @DWUhlfelderLaw I have no party affiliation and I purposefully used a small "l". Politics is something that turns me off altogether. Kind of like engaging on Twitter. Just asking questions yields idiotic responses from random people.

tweet: @JohnnyNeat @DWUhlfelderLaw Nobody who knows me would ever call me a right-winger (or a left-winger). Maybe a libertarian. Pro-freedom, pro-human kindness
